description	"Obi-Wan Kenobi

Class: Jedi
Brief Overview:
A defensive Jedi with a large Force pool that rewards assisting gunners. 

^2Weaponry:
- Melee
- Lightsaber
- Blue/Cyan/Yellow styles
-- Saber/Blaster Defense (3)
-- Blaster Deflect (2)
-- Saber Throw (1) ^3[CS1]
 
^5Force Powers:
- Jump (2)
- Push (2) ^3[CS2]
- Sense (3) ^3[CS3]
- Mind Trick (2) ^3[CS4]

^8Attributes:
- Force Block (1)
- Force Focus (2)

A dedicated and legendary Jedi. Obi-Wan Kenobi fought many battles alongside his apprentice and blood brother, Anakin Skywalker during the Clone Wars. When Skywalker became Darth Vader, Kenobi was forced to duel his former friend and left him dismembered and burning on Mustafar. In his exile on Tatooine, Obi-Wan would learn the path to immortality and set Skywalker's son, Luke, on the path of a Jedi Knight. In the afterlife, Kenobi and Skywalker would meet again as friends."